regulators of the EWS-FLI1 fusion and demonstrated

56
00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:33.930
the importance of the precise levels of these fusion oncoproteins,

57
00:03:34.120 --> 00:03:36.850
opening many new avenues for her research and that of many

58
