and the American Society of Clinical Investigation, and just

84
00:05:15.420 --> 00:05:18.900
this week, induction as a fellow of the AACR

85
00:05:19.060 --> 00:05:19.580
Academy.

86
00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:24.620
Dr. Stegmaier exemplifies the ideal of a consummate clinician

87
00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:28.680
scientist, an unwavering clinical dedication with a highly innovative

88
00:05:28.690 --> 00:05:32.200
and creative research program that has fundamentally advanced the

89
00:05:32.220 --> 00:05:36.060
discovery of therapeutic targets across so many pediatric cancers.

90
00:05:36.100 --> 00:05:39.200
It is really my great pleasure and privilege to introduce the

91
00:05:39.320 --> 00:05:43.100
2026 recipient of the AACR St. Baldrick's Foundation

92
00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:46.720
Award for Outstanding Achievement in Pediatric Cancer Research, Dr.

93
00:05:46.780 --> 00:05:47.720
Kimberly Stegmaier.

