00:08:03.764 --> 00:08:06.104
Gary is shown here in the blue shirt.

129
00:08:06.844 --> 00:08:10.244
And Todd Golub was a postdoctoral fellow at the time.

130
00:08:11.064 --> 00:08:13.604
And George Barker is the young man in the middle.

