00:45:15.004 --> 00:45:17.824
This to me is also what makes this job so fun.

748
00:45:18.104 --> 00:45:20.604
I want to thank our many funding sources over the years.

749
00:45:21.304 --> 00:45:23.964
We surely couldn't do this without them.

