00:48:10.184 --> 00:48:13.054
So I think that we need to continue to push on that.

801
00:48:13.124 --> 00:48:16.964
And I showed one strategy, which is looking for glu-like degraders.

802
00:48:17.024 --> 00:48:20.934
There are other teams that are looking for direct ligands using DEL screens

803
00:48:20.944 --> 00:48:24.194
