00:48:24.804 --> 00:48:28.724
I think this question around bifunctionals and some of the work that we

805
00:48:28.764 --> 00:48:30.964
talked about around this RIP-TAG idea,

806
00:48:31.924 --> 00:48:35.904
I think is very intriguing. So there were some nice presentations here on these

