817
00:49:10.620 --> 00:49:13.860
But I think that there's so many interesting things we could try now.

818
00:49:14.940 --> 00:49:17.339
But we're going to have to define the rules, I think, as we go.

819
00:49:17.600 --> 00:49:19.240
But yeah, great question. I'm open.

